  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc7\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I hope Ranjan will be released soon - Sajith Premadasa",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa said that he hopes that humanitarian politician Ranjan Ramanayake will get full release soon.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition said this while speaking to the media after visiting former Member of Parliament Ranjan Ramanayake in Welikada prison on Saturday.",
        "Ranjan Ramanayake is waiting with positive expectation that he will get full release soon. It is my hope and that of the entire Sri Lankan people that he should be fully released. We pray for this. As per our prayers, we hope that he will get full release soon, not long days.",
        "We are waiting for Ranjan Ramanayake, who is everyone's expectation before long days, to get complete release and we are waiting for that day to come. He is a true philanthropist and a people's artist and has accomplished great works.",
        "Ranjan Ramanayake, a humanitarian politician and popular artist who continues to influence the people, said that our only aim is to see him return to the society as a free citizen and strive for social justice with determination."
      ],
